To our family, our bridal party, and all our honoured guests….thank you for creating memories with us that we’ll cherish for a lifetime 💫

To say the second half of 2022 for me has been a whirlwind, is an understatement. Engaged to the love of my life in July, with 5 months to plan this wedding and 2 wedding dresses to make 🫣 This wedding consumed our 2022 but was everything we could have dreamed of and more 💫

2022 has been good to us…can’t wait to see what next year has in store🤩🥂💫

Wishing everyone a beautiful and blessed 2023 🫶
